          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2383Step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the wedges are cooking, peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>dried sage</strong>, a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> and 50ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>,<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your<strong> sage & onion stuffing</strong></p>",
