    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chicken breast strips </strong>and cook for 10-12 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
