        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
