    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred apart using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Carefully slice the <strong>warmed ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
