            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2383Step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Assemble your sarnie by filling up the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> with a dollop of <strong>mayo</strong>, a handful of<strong> salad</strong>, the <strong>pulled chicken</strong>, <strong>sage & onion stuffing</strong> and some <strong>spiced plum chutney </strong>– this is your<strong> chicken & stuffing sarnie</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chicken & stuffing sarnies</strong> with the <strong>remaining salad, cherry tomato halves</strong> and <strong>potato wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> balsamic dressing</strong> over the salad</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
